title: what about FlyQuest?
body: i have been a huge C9 fan for a while now and was really excited to be able to support both C9 and FlyQuest this season by purchasing both summoner icons when they went on sale but i dont see the one for FlyQuest listed. Will it become available later on or is this a minor mistake?

replies.body: They FlyQuest icon isn't available just yet.  Per the [announcement ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/store/sales/fandom-favs-unlock-esports-team-icon)page, it's aimed to become available in the next patch.  Let me know if that clears things up!
ok awesome! i must have missed that! thanks so much!!!!
